body:
### About Us
EDCD is a group of developers to create and maintain 3rd party tools and sites for Elite:Dangerous.

### Live Chat
You can chat to us on [HipChat](https://www.hipchat.com/gHjMQ9rkZ) and sign up to chat on all E:D HipChat groups [here](https://elite-dangerous.hipchat.com/invite/74670/a3af7ea57008362d83d05fada09bdf84).
